00:00:04.440 --> 00:00:05.720
What is term insurance?

00:00:05.720 --> 00:00:07.480
Term insurance is that

00:00:07.480 --> 00:00:08.600
In case of your death,

00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:10.440
A large amount is given to your family

00:00:10.440 --> 00:00:12.320
by the insurance company on your behalf.

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:14.298
This term insurance is as important, 

00:00:14.298 --> 00:00:16.199
As having your Aadhar card

00:00:16.199 --> 00:00:17.809
Like having your Voter ID card.

00:00:17.809 --> 00:00:20.199
